This program:
        1.  a buffer(1&2) is created that can handle 16 kilobytes of data

            argv? (include usage)
        2.  user input for a file to read.

            if != NULL ...
        3.  open input for reading and output for writing

           start loop !< 0
                4.  read 16384 bytes of data into buffer
                5.  move 1 byte at a time to buffer 2 till complete.
                6.  move buffer 2 to output file
        7.  close files


